description: Hades is the most feared god and is described by Homer and Hesiod as the 'merciless' Hades, sinister and full of evil aura. Hades is the name of the ancient Greek god of the underworld or Pluto in the Roman version and the name of a dark place under the earth that is considered the ultimate destination for the souls of the dead. It is from this background that I want to raise Hades into a darkart illustration. Most people raised common gods like Zeus, Hercules and others. But they rarely heard of Hades. From this illustration I want to introduce the god Hades.
